<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.5">
<l>kaṇṇapi rāṉaiviṇṇōr karumāṇikkat taiyamutai</l>
<l>naṇṇiyu naṇṇakillē ṉaṭuvēyō ruṭampiliṭṭu</l>
<l>tiṇṇa maḻuntakkaṭṭip palaceyviṉai vaṉkayiṟṟāl</l>
<l>puṇṇai maṟaiyavarin teṉaippōravait tāypuṟamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although nearing lord Kṛṣṇa,the black ruby of the celestials,</l>
<l>the ambrosia, I cannot stay near. In the middle you have placed [me] into a body,</l>
<l>tying [me] firmly [and] tightly by the strong rope of many deeds done,</l>
<l>smearing the wound so that it is hidden, you placed me outside to fight.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
